<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Official_church_websites">Official church websites</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=The_Church_of_Jesus_Christ_of_Latter-day_Saints&amp;action=edit&amp;section=29" title="Edit section: Official church websites">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>
<ul>
<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://mormon.org/">mormon.org</a> – Official church website – with information about basic beliefs.</li>
<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://lds.org/">lds.org</a> – Official church website – with links to Gospel Library, Church History, Family Home Evening programs, family history research, and more.</li>
<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.mormonnewsroom.org/">mormonnewsroom.org</a> – Official church website - with current news on the church's official statements.</li>
<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://mormonchannel.org/">Mormon Channel</a> – Official media site with audio and video publications including podcasts and Mormon Messages content.</li>
<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.mormonsandgays.org/">mormonsandgays.org</a> – Official site about the LDS Church's view on homosexuality.</li>
<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.mormonsandchina.org/">mormonsandchina.org</a> – Official site that helps Chinese people who want to act out their faith.</li>
</ul>
<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Reference_sites_and_indexes">Reference sites and indexes</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=The_Church_of_Jesus_Christ_of_Latter-day_Saints&amp;action=edit&amp;section=30" title="Edit section: Reference sites and indexes">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>
